  "method": [
    "Heat the oil in a skillet over the medium heat.",
    "Put in tomato paste, cumin, flour, onion powder, garlic powder, and",
    "chili powder, and cook for one minute.",
    "Add broth, and bring it to boil. Cook for 8-10 minutes until it gets",
    "slightly thickened.",
    "Add pepper and salt to taste and put it aside.",
    "Put spinach in a pan and heat for 2 minutes over the medium heat.",
    "Take a bowl, and mix black beans, vegan cheese, wilted spinach,",
    "green onions, corn, cilantro, and cumin.",
    "Preheat the oven to 375",
    "C. Spray a baking dish, and add some sauce",
    "to the bottom.",
    "Fill tortillas with the mixture, and roll-up.",
    "Pour the remaining sauce on top of enchiladas.",
    "Add 1/4 cup of cheese on the top.",
    "Bake it for 20 minutes, garnish with green onions and cilantro.",
    "Serve and Enjoy!"
  ],
